<div class="uk-section" id="about">
    <div class="uk-container">
        <h2 class="uk-text-center uk-margin-remove cela-text-blue"><strong>CALL FOR REUNION 2021
                ACADEMY</strong></h2>
        <h4 class="uk-text-center uk-text-italic uk-margin-remove cela-text-blue"><strong>KUTAISI INTERNATIONAL
                UNIVERSITY</strong></h4>
        <h4 class="uk-text-center uk-text-italic uk-margin-remove cela-text-blue"><strong>Kutaisi, Georgia</strong></h4>
        <h4 class="uk-text-center uk-margin-remove cela-text-red"><strong>11 - 13 AUGUST 2021</strong></h4>
        <p></p>
        <div>
            <p>It gives us great pleasure to announce that this summer we are planning to hold the CELA 15 Leadership
                Academy which was postponed last year due to the global pandemic. CELA Board members approved Kutaisi
                International University in Kutaisi, Georgia as a new host for the Leadership Academy. We are excited
                about our new venue and have no doubt that CELA 15 participants will have a transformative experience at
                the Academy scheduled for August 2-11, 2021.</p>

            <p>We ask all CELA 15 finalists to confirm their participation to me by replying to info@celanetwork.org.
                Please include your full name, country and contact information in the body of the message. A call for
                facilitators will go out soon. All CELA, SIBF, MELA and SEALA members will be invited to apply and be a
                part of the Academy this summer. CELA is also thrilled to announce that the Georgia team is planning to
                host a reunion at the end of the Academy which will also be held at Kutaisi International University.
                The preliminary dates for the reunion are August 11-13, 2021. The overlapping of the reunion with the
                last day of the Academy will give CELA members a chance to meet the newest members and show the power of
                CELA in their first days as full members of our growing network.
            </p>
            <p>We look forward to seeing many of you in person at the Academy and the reunion. You will be hearing more
                from our team in the coming weeks. </p>


            <h4 class="uk-text-center uk-text-bold cela-text-red uk-margin-remove-bottom">DEADLINE FOR SUBMISSION: 23
                MAY 2021</h4>
            <h4 class="uk-text-center uk-text-bold uk-margin-remove">You will be notified of the committee’s decision no
                later than 29 May 2021</h4>
        </div>
        <div class="uk-margin-medium-top uk-text-italic">
            <h4 class="uk-text-center uk-text-bold uk-margin-remove-bottom cela-text-red">IMPORTANT!</h4>
            CELA 15 Academy will be held amid the ongoing global pandemic which will require safety measures that will
            help prevent the spread of infections among participants, facilitators, faculty and staff. Everybody
            planning to be a part of the CELA 15 Academy should expect to be tested upon the arrival to the KIU campus.
            Additional testing will likely be done during the Academy. Everybody will also be asked to be vaccinated if
            COVID-19 vaccines are available in the countries before the Academy. Additional restrictions may also be
            placed in terms of arrivals to and departures from the KIU campus to prevent any risks of infections.
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
{{#if showAppForm }}
<hr class="uk-divider-icon">
<div class="uk-section" id="applicationForm">
    <div class="uk-container">
        <h2 class="uk-text-center" style="color: #043191"><strong>APPLICATION FORM FOR <br>REUNION 2021</strong></h2>
        <br><br><br>
        <form class="uk-form" action="" method="POST" id="applicationFormData">
            <fieldset class="uk-fieldset">
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Full Name <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <input class="uk-input" type="text" placeholder="First Name, Last Name" name="fullName"
                        id="fullName">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Network name <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <select class="uk-select" name="networkName" id="networkName">
                        <option value="null">Select your network name</option>
                        {{#networks}}
                        <option value="{{this}}">{{this}}</option>
                        {{/networks}}
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Network class year <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <select class="uk-select" name="networkClassYear" id="networkClassYear">
                        <option value="null">Select your network year</option>
                        {{#classYears}}
                        <option value="{{this}}">{{this}}</option>
                        {{/classYears}}
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Country of citizenship <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <select class="uk-select" name="countryCitizen" id="countryCitizen">
                        <option value="null">Select your country of citizenship</option>
                        {{#countries}}
                        <option value="{{this}}">{{this}}</option>
                        {{/countries}}
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Current residence <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <input class="uk-input" type="text" placeholder="Your answer" name="currentResidence"
                        id="currentResidence">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Date of Birth <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <input class="uk-input" type="text" placeholder="Your answer" name="DoB" id="DoB">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Job title <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <input class="uk-input" type="text" placeholder="Your answer" name="title" id="title">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Company name <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <input class="uk-input" type="text" placeholder="Your answer" name="companyName" id="companyName">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Company Industry <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <input class="uk-input" type="text" placeholder="Your answer" name="companyIndustry"
                        id="companyIndustry">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin uk-margin-remove-top">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">E-mail <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <input class="uk-input" type="text" placeholder="Your answer" name="email" id="email">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Phone Number <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <input class="uk-input" type="text"
                        placeholder="Enter your phone number (include a country & city code)" name="phone" id="phone">
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Please share your updated bio <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <textarea class="uk-textarea" rows="5" placeholder="Your answer (no longer than 250 words)"
                        name="bio" id="bio"></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">All sessions are conducted in English, so
                        full fluency in English is critical. If English is not your native language, how would you
                        describe your ability to communicate in English? <span class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <textarea class="uk-textarea" rows="5" placeholder="Your answer" name="isEnglish"
                        id="isEnglish"></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Please describe why you want to be a
                        facilitator and why you think you would be an effective facilitator. <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <textarea class="uk-textarea" rows="5" placeholder="Your answer" name="whyYouFacilitator"
                        id="whyYouFacilitator"></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Please describe your previous
                        facilitating/teaching/moderating/training experiences: (paid/non-paid). If any, please let us
                        know when, with whom and the nature of your role. * <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <textarea class="uk-textarea" rows="5" placeholder="Your answer" name="experienceInfo"
                        id="experienceInfo"></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">If you have been a facilitator at one of the
                        Network Academies, please tell us which class and who were your co-facilitators. <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <textarea class="uk-textarea" rows="5" placeholder="Your answer" name="whoFacilitator"
                        id="whoFacilitator"></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">Please provide 2 references (with contact
                        details) as to your ability to facilitate. If at all possible, make these references members of
                        one of these affiliated networks. <span class="uk-text-danger">*</span></label>
                    <textarea class="uk-textarea" rows="5" placeholder="Your answer" name="references"
                        id="references"></textarea>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <label class="uk-form-label" for="form-stacked-select">
                        If accepted to facilitate, are we authorized to use your photos and bio within our promotional
                        materials? <span class="uk-text-danger">*</span>
                    </label>
                    <div class="uk-margin uk-grid-small uk-child-width-auto uk-grid">
                        <label><input class="uk-radio" type="radio" name="authPhotos" id="acceptYes" value="yes">
                            Yes</label>
                        <label><input class="uk-radio" type="radio" name="authPhotos" id="acceptNo" value="no">
                            No</label>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <hr class="uk-divider-icon">

                <div class="uk-margin uk-text-italic">
                    <p>I understand that the CELA Academy is an intensive leadership development program that requires
                        my full-time commitment as a facilitator for nearly 2 weeks, up to 14 hours a day, in the
                        service of the program, the participants and their needs. I further understand that I have a
                        special responsibility to be a positive leadership role model and network ambassador and that my
                        actions will be reflective of my commitment at all times. The attendance period includes the
                        Facilitator Academy, starting with the opening dinner on the evening of 30 July, and the entire
                        10-day Academy through graduation and the final dinner on 11 August. <span
                            class="uk-text-danger">Additionally, I commit to participate in the monthly pre-LA
                            Facilitator Corps virtual meetings.</span></p>
                    <p>I also understand that I am responsible for arranging my travel to and from Tbilis and that CELA
                        will provide transportation to and from the airport to the University, and my lodging and food
                        expenses from 30 July to 12 August. All other expenses are my responsibility.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="uk-margin">
                    <div class="uk-grid">
                        <div class="uk-width-auto@m uk-first-column">
                            <input class="uk-checkbox cela-checkbox-red" type="checkbox" id="chkAgreement"
                                name="chkAgreement">
                        </div>
                        <div class="uk-width-expand@m uk-text-light uk-text-small">
                            I understand and commit to the terms stated above: <span class="uk-text-danger">*</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="uk-card uk-card-default uk-card-body uk-width-1-1@m uk-margin uk-padding-small cela-error uk-hidden"
                    id="applicationErrorBox">
                    <p>Please complete all fields!</p>
                </div>
                <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{csrfToken}}">
                <input type="submit" href="#" class="uk-button uk-button-large uk-width-1-1 uk-button-primary"
                    id="sendBtn" value="Submit Application" disabled></input>

            </fieldset>
    </div>




    </form>


</div>
{{/if}}
</div>

